{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a7beeece66","title":"关于四川文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"859fcbf03f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"a7beeece66"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c42c8c4e2","type":"title","text":"关于四川文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a7beeece66"},{"id":"fd8ddb6876","type":"paragraph","text":"从宜宾问题的揭发，才开始揭开了四川阶级斗争盖子的序幕，才开始揭开季井泉的盖子。四川文化大革命之所以困难，主要是刘、邓、李井泉搞的，他们把刘结挺打成反革命，把他们开除出党，这次才翻过来。以后要把这个材料印出来，发给每个党员。四川阶级斗争的揭盖子，两条路线斗争还未解决。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a7beeece66"}],"page":{"id":"fb096f1acb","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a7beeece66","start":427,"end":427}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"088913a740","type":"title","text":"关于四川文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a7beeece66"},{"id":"6a7d9f610e","type":"paragraph","text":"从宜宾问题的揭发，才开始揭开了四川阶级斗争盖子的序幕，才开始揭开李井泉的盖子。四川文化大革命之所以困难，主要是刘、邓、李井泉搞的，他们把刘结挺打成反革命，把他们开除出党，这次才翻过来。以后要把这个材料印出来，发给每个党员。四川阶级斗争的揭盖子，两条路线斗争还未解决。（摘自林彪同志 1967 年 4 月 5 日关于四川问题的讲话）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a7beeece66"}],"page":{"id":"7278a69e99","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a7beeece66","start":576,"end":576}}}},"__N_SSG":true}